{
  "page": "Doreah",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the Sand Snake, see <a href=\"/index.php/Dorea_Sand\" title=\"Dorea Sand\">Dorea Sand</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/50px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/75px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/100px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Doreah</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/50px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/75px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/100px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Doreah.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Doreah.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/1/17/Doreah.jpg/350px-Doreah.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"446\" srcset=\"/images/1/17/Doreah.jpg 1.5x\" /></a><div>Art by Foolish-Arethousa</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>'s <i>khalasar</i></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lysene</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_278_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">278&#160;AC</a> or <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_279_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">279&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafdoreah.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafdoreah.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/299_AC\" title=\"299 AC\">299&#160;AC</a><br />the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_waste\" title=\"Red waste\">red waste</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (mentioned)</li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">Played by</span></th><td>\nRoxanne McKee</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\"><span style=\"white-space:nowrap\">TV series</span></th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: <br /><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_1\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 1\">Season 1</a> | <a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones_-_Season_2\" title=\"Game of Thrones - Season 2\">2</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Doreah</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lysene</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Handmaid\" title=\"Handmaid\">handmaid</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a>.\n</p><p>In the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>, Doreah is portrayed by <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Roxanne_McKee\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Roxanne McKee\">Roxanne McKee</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Doreah\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Doreah</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Doreah\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Doreah</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Doreah&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<dl><dd><i>See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Doreah\" title=\"Category:Images of Doreah\">Images of Doreah</a></i></dd></dl>\n<p>Doreah has blue eyes<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and soft white skin.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Her soft<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> blond hair<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> is fair<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> and golden.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> At the start of the series, she is almost twenty.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Doreah is an attentive<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup> handmaid experienced in <a href=\"/index.php/Pillow_house\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Pillow house\">pillow tricks</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> and the arts of love.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Doreah&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Magister <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio Mopatis</a> found Doreah in a <a href=\"/index.php/Pleasure_house\" title=\"Pleasure house\">pleasure house</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a> bedded her while he was a guest at <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio%27s_manse\" title=\"Illyrio&#39;s manse\">Illyrio's manse</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Pentos\" title=\"Pentos\">Pentos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Doreah&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Doreah&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Doreah, <a href=\"/index.php/Irri\" title=\"Irri\">Irri</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Jhiqui\" title=\"Jhiqui\">Jhiqui</a>, are given to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Wedding_of_Drogo_and_Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Wedding of Drogo and Daenerys Targaryen\">wedding gifts</a> to serve as her handmaidens; Doreah is to instruct the young bride in the \"womanly\" arts of love.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> Daenerys remembers Doreah's lessons when she sleeps with Khal <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a> is usually kinder to Doreah than to Daenerys's <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a> handmaids, and Daenerys has the Lyseni sew a fine sandsilk cloak for her brother. When Daenerys sends Doreah to bring Viserys to dinner, however, he strikes the handmaid. Daenerys then offers the cloak to her brother, but Viserys refuses to wear the Dothraki garb.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Doreah drapes Daenerys in a scented sandsilk robe after she has sex with Drogo by the <a href=\"/index.php/Womb_of_the_World\" title=\"Womb of the World\">Womb of the World</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot46.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The handmaid accompanies Daenerys when she visits the Western Market of <a href=\"/index.php/Vaes_Dothrak\" title=\"Vaes Dothrak\">Vaes Dothrak</a>. At a <a href=\"/index.php/Magic\" title=\"Magic\">magician</a>'s booth, Daenerys purchases a fertility charm for Doreah. When a wineseller attacks Daenerys, Doreah prevents the pregnant girl from falling on her belly.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot54.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Daenerys claims <a href=\"/index.php/Eroeh\" title=\"Eroeh\">Eroeh</a> and tasks Doreah with tending to her wounds.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Daenaerys's handmaids help treat Drogo as the <i>khal</i> is dying.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup> Doreah washes and brushes Daenerys's hair in preparation for Drogo's funeral.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Doreah&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After <a href=\"/index.php/Drogo\" title=\"Drogo\">Drogo</a>'s death, Daenerys takes what remains of her <i><a href=\"/index.php/Khalasar\" title=\"Khalasar\">khalasar</a></i> and marches out into the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_waste\" title=\"Red waste\">red waste</a> in search of a safe place. On the march, Doreah dies of a wasting disease,.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok12.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Doreah&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Daenerys, now <a href=\"/index.php/Queen_of_Meereen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Queen of Meereen\">Queen of Meereen</a>, uses Doreah's lessons when she sleeps with <a href=\"/index.php/Daario_Naharis\" title=\"Daario Naharis\">Daario Naharis</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;13&#93;</a></sup> Having reluctantly reopened the <a href=\"/index.php/Fighting_pits_of_Meereen\" title=\"Fighting pits of Meereen\">fighting pits of Meereen</a>, Daenerys thinks of Doreah and other women she has lost.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_14-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd50.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-14\">&#91;14&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Doreah\">Quotes by Doreah</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Doreah&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Doreah\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Once there were two <a href=\"/index.php/Moon\" title=\"Moon\">moons</a> in the sky, but one wandered too close to the <a href=\"/index.php/Sun\" title=\"Sun\">sun</a> and cracked from the heat. A thousand thousand <a href=\"/index.php/Dragon\" title=\"Dragon\">dragons</a> poured forth, and drank the fire of the sun. That is why dragons <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonflame\" title=\"Dragonflame\">breathe flame</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Doreah to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Doreah\">Quotes about Doreah</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Doreah&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Doreah\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>She's very good, <a href=\"/index.php/Illyrio_Mopatis\" title=\"Illyrio Mopatis\">Illyrio</a> and I can both swear to that.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Viserys_Targaryen\" title=\"Viserys Targaryen\">Viserys Targaryen</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lysene</a> girl had hair the color of <a href=\"/index.php/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">honey</a>, and eyes like the summer sky.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot23.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Doreah&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i>See the <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest/Calculations_Ages#Doreah\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest/Calculations Ages\">Doreah</a> calculation.</i></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafdoreah.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafdoreah.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>, Doreah.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-2\">3.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-3\">3.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot11.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-4\">3.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_11\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 11\">Chapter 11</a>, Daenerys II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot36.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B